export const sourceCode = "---\ntitle: CLI\n---\n\n# CLI\n\n```bash\ntelekinesis <command> [options]\n```\n\n| Command | What it does |\n| --- | --- |\n| `record <sheet>` | Record a demo — `--format mp4 \\| gif \\| both` |\n| `gif <sheet>` | Record and export a looping GIF |\n| `preview <sheet>` | Open a headed browser and perform the sheet (no file) |\n| `studio` | Launch the [Studio](/studio) editor (`--port`, `--target`) |\n| `init` | Scaffold a starter timesheet |\n| `sounds` | Synthesize a starter sound pack with ffmpeg |\n\n## record\n\n```bash\ntelekinesis record flow.timesheet.json -o demo.mp4          # MP4 (default)\ntelekinesis record flow.timesheet.json --format both        # MP4 + GIF\ntelekinesis record flow.timesheet.json -u http://localhost:3000?demo\n```\n\nOptions: `-o/--output`, `-f/--format`, `-u/--url`, `-s/--sounds`,\n`--gif-fps`, `--gif-width`, `--no-gifski`, `--headed`, `--keep-temp`.\n\n## Packages\n\n| Package | Role |\n| --- | --- |\n| `@telekinesis/schema` | Zod effects + timesheet + `layoutTimesheet` — the shared contract |\n| `@telekinesis/core` | `<TelekineticFrame>`, `<TelekinesisStage>`, runtime, Studio bridge |\n| `@telekinesis/engine` | Playwright recorder → silent video + `audio-map.json` |\n| `@telekinesis/render` | ffmpeg: audio mixing (MP4) + GIF export |\n| `@telekinesis/cli` | `record` / `gif` / `preview` / `studio` / `init` / `sounds` |\n| `@telekinesis/mcp` | MCP server for AI-authored timesheets |";
